room_title: Escape room "The Dream" by Wichita Room Escape in Wichita
room_description: You have awakened from a deep sleep... or have you? Things don't seem to be where you left them and your surroundings aren't as they should be. You will need to shake this sleep off and gather your wits about you to find the lucidity you will need to get out of this one. Is the ticking clock your alarm getting ready to jolt you out of your dream? Or is it the pending doom of failure to escape this unusual surrounding?
